			<h2 class="underlined-heading blue-underlined">Authoritative Application Repository</h2>
			<p>Brinqa Application Risk Management helps establish an authoritative inventory by providing a ready-to-use application repository template that can serve as the golden- source for application inventory. Existing sources may be leveraged using Brinqa data connectors to common asset management, CMDB or proprietary systems to populate the golden source.</p>			
