			<div class="text-center-xs col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 additional-y-spacing wow fadeInUp">
				<h2 class="underlined-heading blue-underlined">Integrated Business Context</h2>
				<p>An effective application risk management program factors this distinction into its risk evaluation methodology to ensure that risks and threats are rated based on business impact and not merely on security or technical requirements. Brinqa Application Security Risk Management solution promotes this by providing features in the application repository template to capture, maintain and represent this information. Alternatively, inherent risk assessments may be conducted to evaluate business relevance and impact if this information is not currently maintained or established in the organization.</p>				
				<br>
				<!-- <a href="#" class="brinqa-btn filled-blue-btn" >Learn More</a> -->
