	<section class="text-section greyed bordered-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center-xs col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 additional-y-spacing wow fadeInUp">
				<h2 class="underlined-heading blue-underlined">Issue Identification & Remediation</h2>
				<p>Gaps and threats identified during any step of the application development or risk evaluation process may be converted into issues to be tracked for remediation. The integrated Brinqa Risk and Control Framework provides clear guidelines to developers or application owners about the actions that may be taken to remediate a problem. The controls framework also empowers program owners to demonstrate compliance with industry standards and regulations such as PCI, SOX, FISMA etc.</p>				
				<br>
				<!-- <a href="#" class="brinqa-btn filled-blue-btn" >Learn More</a> -->
